<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_123_r2l7"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> wılhelm / es ſınd ʒwen des Judenrats auf heẅt für vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l8"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns geſagt / daʒ auf dem tag ʒu Mergentheim nıchts geendt ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l9">vmb dıe ſache als dır <expan>wıſſenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / Es hab <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> Moſſe ganns von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l10">Bıſchofſheim <expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> Jren genoſʒen . <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıben</expan> / wıe er ſeıd <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tags </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l11">dıe ſache daniden ʒured bracht hab / vnd er hoffe dıe ſache wurd mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l12">ııȷ<hi rend="sup">C</hi> oder ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">C</hi> <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> abgeen daʒ vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>ſtepf<ex>an</ex></expan> von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l13">Juden ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchrybe nach <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> notdurft alſo <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır niht <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l14">wır wölten dır das ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> tun / daʒ du dıch weſt deſt bas darnach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l15">ʒurıchten / Doch daʒ du dıchs nıht ſolt <expan>hınd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> an der <expan>fertıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l16">als du von vns <expan>geſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> bıſt / des wır vns ʒu dır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> Auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l18"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır dır <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> dıe </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_123_line_1577033038774_1571">ein </ab></add> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> des vıcʒtums von <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l19">brıef / Als wır Jm von yoſep pücʒels Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_123_r2l20"><expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex>ſıgıllo</expan> Erhardȷ ſchurſtab <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuiu<ex>m</ex></expan> / <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>aſce<ex>n</ex>ſıo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> </ab>
